  "name": "RPlog_Templars_Allies_versus_Pirates_-_Part_1",
  "title": "Gunboat Diplomacy in the Asteroid Belt",
  "summary": "In the hangar of the Templar, Colonel Eckhart briefs his marines and civilian allies on a mission to wipe out pirates operating from an asteroid mining base. Commandeering the reluctant diplomat Hal Seiser's combat shuttle the Olive Branch, piloted by Tiaryn with the quartermaster Siarra, the soldier Samyok, the gunner Cort, and the Quarren medic Druze aboard, the team micro-jumps in escorted by the X-wing pilots Wrexan and Bobloblow. They emerge to find Weequay pirates in Y-TIE 'uglies' ambushing them, and a running firefight erupts amid the asteroids. As Tiaryn dodges rocks and fire and the turret gunners shred the uglies one by one, Eckhart orders the panicking, airsick Hal onto the comms to bluff the pirates into surrender. Hal's improvised threats and a heavily armed RX4 patrol craft's destruction by the X-wings' proton torpedoes break the pirates' nerve. The asteroid base broadcasts its surrender, and Eckhart orders the team to go in, cuff the pirates, scavenge gear, and level the facility.",
